        {
            "id": 6008907,
            "title": "通膨壓力緩 5月CPI年增率降至1.55% 創逾4年來低點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主計總處今 (5) 日公布 5 月消費者物價總指數 (CPI) 年增幅 1.55%，創 2021 年 4 月以來新低，主要是因油價下跌，而前 5 月平均 CPI 年增率降至 2.04%，有望逐漸拋開 2% 通膨警戒。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008907%2Fl%2Fcbddf78488b13695c2900ac4b549b014.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">通膨警戒逐漸解除。(圖：主計總處提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主計總處認為，隨著國際原物料價格走跌，且<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>升值使進口成本下降，下半年 CPI 增幅可望低於 2%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主計總處統計，5 月肉類、外食費等食物類價格持續上漲，水果價格仍較去年高，房租、掛號費、補習及學習費、汽車保養及修理等費用也調升，惟蔬菜、蛋類、油料費、運輸費、通訊費和成衣等價格下跌，抵銷部分漲幅。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>若扣除蔬菜水果，5 月 CPI 年增 1.34%，再剔除能源後的總指數 (即核心 CPI) 漲 1.61%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察 368 個查價項目，價格較去年同期上漲較多者有番石榴漲 103.93%、金飾及珠寶漲 21.44%、胃腸藥漲 11.61%、豬肉漲 6.90%、視唱中心費用漲 5.62%、診所掛號費漲 5.57%、其他食用油 (橄欖油等) 漲 5.37%、中式麵食 (如炒麵、小籠包) 漲 4.23%、安親課輔費漲 3.76%、中式米食 (如便當、滷肉飯) 漲 3.60%、火鍋漲 3.40%、住宅管理費漲 3.12% 等。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img alt=\"圖表：主計總處提供。\" data-height=\"363\" data-mime=\"image/png\" data-ratio=\"1.7245179063360883\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6008907/m/5c2fefb96bd82fa446ef9c58a1914149.jpg\" data-width=\"626\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6008907/l/5c2fefb96bd82fa446ef9c58a1914149.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption>圖表：主計總處提供。</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>就七大類來看，食物類漲 3.09%，主因水果供量較少價格上漲 18.56%，肉類、外食費也漲 4.80%、3.50%，惟蛋類下跌 13.37%，蔬菜價格跌 10.92%，抵銷部分漲幅。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雜項類漲 2.44%，主因金飾及珠寶等個人隨身用品上漲 6.52%，部分個人照顧服務因饋贈端午禮金，加上香菸及檳榔等價格上漲。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>醫藥保健類漲 2.18%，反映部分醫療院所調升掛號費、病房自付費，與假牙及矯正費等費用，醫療費用上漲 2.58%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而居住類漲 1.80%，則因房租上漲 2.28%、家庭管理費用上漲 3.85%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>交通及通訊類跌 1.56%，主因油料費及通訊費分別下跌 8.15%、2.32%，惟交通工具零件及維修費上漲 2.03%，抵銷部分跌幅。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，觀察主要國家 (地區) 物價變化，日本漲 3.6%，美國漲 2.3%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>區漲 2.2%，南韓漲 2.1%，香港漲 2.0%，新加坡漲 0.9%，中國跌 0.1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
